Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.55,0:00:04.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好久不见
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.12,0:00:07.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个…祝你早日康复
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.71,0:00:09.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哇 好漂亮
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.41,0:00:12.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你还记得我喜欢什么花哦
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.23,0:00:18.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思 突然叫你来
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.34,0:00:21.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,坐吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.75,0:00:26.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,合唱部在今年的比赛中又得金奖了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.33,0:00:27.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我看了报纸哦
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.07,0:00:31.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在不叫合唱部了 叫声乐部
